OL,5,G2340 Ups and Downs of a Handyman
OL,6,     FWhen Bob becomes a handyman in the
OL,7,     Fquiet village of Chipping Sodbury,
OL,8,     Fhe soon finds all his customers
OL,9,     Fare women. Their endless jobs keep
OL,10,     Fhim busy and leave Bob wondering
OL,11,     Fhow hell keep up!
